# Frontend env. Vite only exposes vars prefixed with VITE_.
#
# By default, src/lib/api.js falls back to the deployed Railway backend:
#   https://imaginative-spontaneity-production.up.railway.app
# So you don't need an .env file to run `npm run dev` — the fallback works.
#
# Override only when you want to hit a *local* backend instead. Use
# .env.local (also gitignored) so it doesn't override per-environment
# Railway settings:
#
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
